@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### 2.1 Crear Inventario #1 - Laptop
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventario
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "LAPTOP-DELL-001",
  "nombre": "Laptop Dell XPS 13",
  "cantidad": 50
}

